THis blog app includes the following basic functionalities:

User registration and authentication: Users can create an account, log in, and manage their profile.
Blog creation: Users can create new blog posts, including a title, content, and images or videos.
Blog editing: Users can modify existing blog posts by editing the title, content, or other details.
Blog deletion: Users can delete blog posts that are no longer needed or relevant.
Commenting: Users can leave comments on blog posts and engage in discussions with other users.
Blog search: Users can search for blog posts based on keywords, categories, or other criteria.
Content management: The app can include a content management system to manage the blog's layout, categories, tags, and other settings.
